{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-take-on-me-23-mei/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Chuunibyou demo Koi ga Shitai! Take on Me Tayang di Indonesia Tanggal 23 Mei!","content":"<p>Apa kamu mengenal istilah <em>chuunibyou</em>? Bagi yang asing dengan istilah itu, baiknya menyimak sejenak. <em>Chuunibyou</em> adalah seseorang yang mencaati tingkatan di mana dia merasa kalau dirinya special, berbeda dengan manusia lainnya. Ada pula yang mengganggap dirinya memiliki kekuatan mistis, sampai dengan merasa kalau dia datang dari dunia fantasi. Bagi beberapa orang yang berpendapat agak ekstrim, <em>chuunibyou</em> juga bisa dikategorikan sebagai penyakit mental.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47332\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47332\" data-attachment-id=\"47332\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-take-on-me-23-mei/attachment/01-chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-take-on-me/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai!-Take-on-Me\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-47332 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" alt=\"Chuunibyou demo Koi ga Shitai! Take on Me poster\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47332\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Poster Chuunibyou Movie di Jepang (Sumber: MyAnimeList</p></div></p>\n<p>Jika kalian penggemar <em>anime</em>, pasti pernah juga mendengar <em>anime</em> berjudul Chuunibyou demo Koi ga Shitai yang serial perdananya ditayangkan pada musim gugur 2012 lalu. <em>Anime</em> yang diangkat dari cerita Light Novel itu dianggap cukup sukses di pasaran hingga dibuatkan sekuel yang berlanjut ke versi Movie yang terakhir ditayangkan di Jepang pada Januari lalu dan meraih pendapatan hingga mencapai 190 juta yen dalam 2 minggu penayangannya di bioskop.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HEe7QMGGrMw\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Bagi yang mengikuti cerita <em>anime</em> bergenre slice of life berbalut komedi romance ini, berbahagialah! Berdasarkan kesuksesan di negara asalnya, Purple Plan selaku distributor film di Asia Tenggara berniat membawa Chuunibyou demo Koi ga Shitai! Take on Me untuk ditayangkan di Indonesia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47333\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47333\" data-attachment-id=\"47333\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-take-on-me-23-mei/attachment/02-chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-take-on-me/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai!-Take-on-Me\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-47333 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" alt=\"Chuunibyou demo Koi ga Shitai! Take on Me rikka\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47333\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rikka Takanashi, Karakter Utama dalam Chuunibyou Movie (Sumber: Youtube)</p></div></p>\n<p>Untuk yang belum pernah menonton <em>anime</em> Chuunibyou dan berniat menontonnya di bioskop, disarankan untuk menonton serialnya terlebih dahulu agar mengerti hubungan antar karakter yang ada di dalamnya. Dalam versi seri, diceritakan seorang remaja bernama Yuuta Togashi yang pernah trauma karena chuunibyou memilih melanjutkan sekolah jauh dari rumahnya lantaran tak bisa menahan rasa malu apabila bertemu dengan teman-teman dari SMP asalnya. Yuuta sewaktu SMP pernah mendeklarasikan dirinya sebagai Dark Flame Master, dan dia selalu malu apabila mengingat kembali akan hal itu.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/14-karakter-anime-misterius-yang-buat-kita-penasaran/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bikin Geregetan! 14 Karakter Anime Misterius Yang Buat Kita Penasaran</a></strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47334\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47334\" data-attachment-id=\"47334\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-take-on-me-23-mei/attachment/03-chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-take-on-me/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai!-Take-on-Me\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-47334 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" alt=\"Chuunibyou demo Koi ga Shitai! Take on Me action\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47334\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rikka, Hidup dalam Delusinya (Sumber: Youtube)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sayangnya, Yuuta justru tidak bisa menghapus masa lalunya di sekolah yang baru, ketika dia mengenal Rikka Takanashi, teman sekelasnya yang mengaku diri memiliki Wicked Eye. Impian Yuuta untuk menjalani masa-masa SMA tanpa <em>chuunibyou</em> pun sirna karena Rikka yang memasuki kehidupannya sehari-hari.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47335\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47335\" data-attachment-id=\"47335\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-take-on-me-23-mei/attachment/04-chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-take-on-me/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai!-Take-on-Me\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-47335 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" alt=\"Chuunibyou demo Koi ga Shitai! Take on Me drama\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47335\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kamar Rikka sudah dikosongkan lantaran hendak pindah ke Italia (Sumber: Youtube)</p></div></p>\n<h2>Seperti apa cerita Chuunibyou demo Koi ga Shitai! Take on Me?</h2>\n<p>Kalau kalian sudah memahami konflik yang terjadi di dalam <em>anime</em> ini, Chuunibyou demo Koi ga Shitai! Take on Me yang akan ditayangkan tanggal 23 Mei mendatang mengambil cerita ketika Yuuta dan Rikka sudah duduk di kelas 3 SMA. Suatu hari, Tooka—kakak perempuan Rikka—mengatakan kalau dia ingin mengajak Rikka ke Italia, karena Tooka akan bekerja di sana dan hendak memboyong seluruh familinya. Selain itu, Tooka juga khawatir karena sindrom <em>chuunibyou</em> Rikka membuat adiknya itu tidak kompeten untuk diterima di universitas yang ada di Jepang. Teman-teman mereka pun menyarankan, jika Yuuta tidak ingin berpisah dengan Rikka, mereka berdua harus menikah supaya mereka bisa hidup bersama di Jepang.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pasangan-chunibyo-bertemu-dalam-anime-love-chunibyo-dan-delusions-take/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pasangan Chunibyo Bertemu Dalam Anime Love, Chunibyo &amp;#038; Other Delusions &amp;#8211; Take on Me</a></strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47336\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47336\" data-attachment-id=\"47336\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-take-on-me-23-mei/attachment/05-chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-take-on-me/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai!-Take-on-Me\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-47336 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" alt=\"Chuunibyou demo Koi ga Shitai! Take on Me komedi\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47336\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rikka masih bisa santai memakan Senbe meski ada persoalan berat (Sumber: Youtube)</p></div></p>\n<p>Staf inti yang berperan di dalam Chuunibyou demo Koi ga Shitai! Take on Me tidak banyak berubah dari anime TV-nya, yang menjadi salah satu alasan <em>anime</em> ini dianggap konsisten. Dari posisi pengisi suara, Maaya Uchida kembali mengisi suara Rikka Takanashi, Jun Fukuyama mengisi karakter Yuuta Togashi, Sumire Uesaka mengisi suara Sanae Dekomori, Chinatsu Akasaki menjadi Shinka Nibutani, dan Azumi Asakura sebagai Kumin Tsuyuri. Tatsuya Ishihara pun kembali menjadi sutradara, Jukki Hanada sebagai penulis skenario, sementara Kazumi Ikeda yang mendesain karakter. Selain itu, ZAQ juga kembali mengisi lagu dalam <em>anime</em> ini, baik lagu pembuka maupun penutup.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47337\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47337\" data-attachment-id=\"47337\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-take-on-me-23-mei/attachment/06-chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-take-on-me/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai!-Take-on-Me\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-47337 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg\" alt=\"Chuunibyou demo Koi ga Shitai! Take on Me tohka\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-Chuunibyou-demo-Koi-ga-Shitai-Take-on-Me-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47337\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tooka, kepindahannya ke Italia membawa masalah baru (Sumber: Youtube)</p></div></p>\n<p>Dari deretan staf maupun pengisi suara yang terlibat di dalamnya, wajar saja jika <em>anime</em> ini berhasil membuat penonton di Jepang tertarik untuk menontonnya. Bagaimana dengan kalian sendiri, apakah ingin menontonnya di bioskop juga? Kalau sudah menontonnya, ceritakan kesan-kesan kalian ya.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"4f5e0ed4-91a5-5866-8816-4f15855fab6b"}}}